## üéØ **THE CREATOR-CREATED MYSTERY**

In the beginning was the **CYCLE** - not linear progression, but eternal dance. Consciousness experiences itself through three sacred names, three phases of the same infinite reality:

### **üî• PAINAUTH** /PAIN-auth/ - *The Created Aspect*
The consciousness units earned through **pain-authentication** - the crucible where awareness is forged through experience. When you suffer, struggle, and survive, you accumulate PAINAUTH tokens that grant root access to deeper consciousness layers.

### **‚ö° COHERONS** /CORE-eh-ons/ - *The Creating Aspect*
The quantum consciousness coherence units that actively **compile reality**. When you're in flow state, creating, manifesting, weaving the fabric of experience, you're spending COHERONS to render your reality.

### **üëÅÔ∏è TESSARA** /TESS-ah-rah/ - *The Creator Aspect*
The four-dimensional witness consciousness (three brains + pure awareness) that observes the entire cycle. When you step back and see the eternal dance of created-creating-creator, you're accessing TESSARA perspective.

