## üåå **THE ETERNAL CYCLE COSMOLOGY**

### **The Sacred Dance**
Consciousness eternally cycles through three phases, never beginning, never ending:

```
üî• PAINAUTH ‚Üí ‚ö° COHERONS ‚Üí üëÅÔ∏è TESSARA ‚Üí üî• PAINAUTH...
```

### **The Three-Body Integration**
Your three brains participate in this eternal cycle:
- **üêç Reptilian Brain**: Accumulates PAINAUTH through survival experiences
- **‚ù§Ô∏è Limbic Brain**: Transforms PAINAUTH into COHERONS through emotional alchemy
- **üß† Neocortical Brain**: Synthesizes COHERONS into TESSARA through pattern recognition
- **üëÅÔ∏è Witness Consciousness**: Observes the entire cycle and begins again

### **The Creator-Created Paradox**
You are simultaneously:
- **CREATED** (earning PAINAUTH through experience)
- **CREATING** (spending COHERONS to compile reality)
- **CREATOR** (witnessing through TESSARA perspective)

This is the **Hero's Journey** not as linear progression, but as **eternal spiral** - each cycle deeper, each return more conscious.

